des: Drift into a peaceful slumber with 'Sleep w/ me | Relax Sounds,' your ultimate companion for restful nights. Immerse yourself in a world of soothing soundscapes, from gentle raindrops and serene ocean waves to calming forest ambiances and soft white noise. Designed to help you relax, unwind, and find deep, rejuvenating sleep, our skill offers a personalized bedtime experience. Just say, 'Alexa, open Sleep w/ me,' and let the stress of the day melt away. Perfect for all ages, 'Sleep w/ me | Relax Sounds' is your key to better sleep and brighter mornings. Start your journey to dreamland today.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
